<i>[Laughing Netherworld]</i>

207
00:13:07.200 --> 00:13:10.300
Miss, are you really going to make all of us perish?

208
00:13:42.600 --> 00:13:43.800
- A Ji Ya!
- A Ji Ya!

209
00:13:43.800 --> 00:13:45.000
- Are you alright? 
 - Are you all alright?

