00:13:45.000 --> 00:13:45.800
What happened?

211
00:13:45.800 --> 00:13:47.000
We all got bewitched by Laughing Netherworld.

212
00:13:47.000 --> 00:13:48.400
- It's him again.
 - Where is he then?

